{
  "stem": "3524.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a great day to go tavern to tavern and make friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a joyous occasion in a way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we remained there for some weeks-- I can't remember the exact period of time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we actually got word that we were to go across the channel to France.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't have any idea what we were going to face there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We boarded some ships with the-- some Italian soldiers that they had gotten from the campaign, and took us overnight to the channel, and entered Le Havre harbor one morning.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember the exact date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was rough in some spots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was done at nighttime, so I really didn't get a chance to see much of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I slept most of the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Le Havre, France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were transported to-- I think the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was called Twenty Grand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a processing camp in-- near Le Havre.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was awe and struck-- awe-inspired by-- I shouldn't say inspired, but when I looked at Le Havre, it looked like a gravel pit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the buildings were pretty well bombed out, and you saw pieces of rubble all over the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the war then became a little more personal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You-- you could see the effects of the allied bombings, and there was hardly anything standing at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Prior to that, we had one furlough in London, and we were-- experienced one of the V bombs that the Germans had gone over.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We weren't hit, but you could hear the-- the whistling of the bomb.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some were sent to bomb shelters at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
